# Input

```scss
$name: fade;
$suffix: loader;

@keyframes  #{$name}{to{opacity:1}}

@keyframes $name{to{opacity:1}}

@keyframes #{$name}-out{to{opacity:1}}

@keyframes fade-#{$suffix}{to{opacity:1}}

```


# Formatted

```scss
$name: fade;
$suffix: loader;

@keyframes #{$name} {
	to {
		opacity: 1;
	}
}

@keyframes $name {
	to {
		opacity: 1;
	}
}

@keyframes #{$name}-out {
	to {
		opacity: 1;
	}
}

@keyframes fade-#{$suffix} {
	to {
		opacity: 1;
	}
}

```
